#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc73:1.1.0"
msgid "73. Mohanasikkhāpada"
msgstr ""
"<hgroup><h1 id=\"Bu-Pc.73\">Monks’ Confession 73: the training rule on "
"deception</h1></hgroup>"

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
#, fuzzy
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc73:1.1.1"
msgid ""
"Tena samayena buddho bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa "
"ārāme."
msgstr ""
"<h2 id=\"nidana\">Origin story</h2><p><a class=\"pts-cs\" id=\"Bu-Pc.73.1\""
">Bu-Pc.73.1</a><a class=\"pts-vp-en\" id=\"BD.3.43\">BD.3.43</a><a class"
"=\"wt-pa\">1329</a>At one time the Buddha was staying at Sāvatthī in the "
"Jeta Grove, Anāthapiṇḍika’s Monastery."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc73:1.1.2"
msgid ""
"Tena kho pana samayena chabbaggiyā bhikkhū anācāraṃ ācaritvā “aññāṇakena "
"āpannāti jānantū”ti pātimokkhe uddissamāne evaṃ vadanti—"
msgstr ""
"At that time the monks from the group of six misbehaved. And they said to "
"each other, “Let’s make the other monks think that we committed these "
"offenses because we didn’t know about the rules.”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc73:1.1.3"
msgid ""
"“idāneva kho mayaṃ jānāma, ayampi kira dhammo suttāgato suttapariyāpanno "
"anvaddhamāsaṃ uddesaṃ āgacchatī”ti."
msgstr ""
"Then, during the recitation of the monastic code, they said, “Just now did "
"we find out that this rule too has come down in the monastic code, is "
"included in the monastic code, and comes up for recitation every half-"
"month.”</p>"

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc73:1.1.4"
msgid "Ye te bhikkhū appicchā … pe …"
msgstr "<p><a class=\"wt-pa\">1330</a>The monks of few desires …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc73:1.1.5"
msgid "te ujjhāyanti khiyyanti vipācenti—"
msgstr "complained and criticized them,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc73:1.1.6"
msgid ""
"“kathañhi nāma chabbaggiyā bhikkhū pātimokkhe uddissamāne evaṃ vakkhanti—"
msgstr ""
"“How can the monks from the group of six, while the monastic code is being "
"recited, say,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc73:1.1.7"
msgid ""
"‘idāneva kho mayaṃ jānāma, ayampi kira dhammo suttāgato suttapariyāpanno "
"anvaddhamāsaṃ uddesaṃ āgacchatī’”ti … pe …"
msgstr ""
"‘Just now did we find out that this rule too has come down in the monastic "
"code, is included in the monastic code, and comes up for recitation every "
"half-month’?” …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc73:1.1.8"
msgid "“saccaṃ kira tumhe, bhikkhave, pātimokkhe uddissamāne evaṃ vadetha—"
msgstr "“Is it true, monks, that you said this?”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc73:1.1.9"
msgid ""
"‘idāneva kho mayaṃ jānāma, ayampi kira dhammo suttāgato suttapariyāpanno "
"anvaddhamāsaṃ uddesaṃ āgacchatī’”ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc73:1.1.10"
msgid "“Saccaṃ, bhagavā”ti."
msgstr "“It’s true, Master.”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc73:1.1.11"
msgid "Vigarahi buddho bhagavā … pe …"
msgstr "The Buddha rebuked them, “…"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc73:1.1.12"
msgid ""
"kathañhi nāma tumhe, moghapurisā, pātimokkhe uddissamāne evaṃ vakkhatha—"
msgstr "Foolish men, while the monastic code is being recited, how can you say,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc73:1.1.13"
msgid ""
"‘idāneva kho mayaṃ jānāma, ayampi kira dhammo suttāgato suttapariyāpanno "
"anvaddhamāsaṃ uddesaṃ āgacchatī’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘Just now did we find out that this rule too has come down in the monastic "
"code, is included in the monastic code, and comes up for recitation every "
"half-month’?"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc73:1.1.14"
msgid "Netaṃ, moghapurisā, appasannānaṃ vā pasādāya … pe …"
msgstr "This will not give rise to confidence in those without it …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc73:1.1.15"
msgid "evañca pana, bhikkhave, imaṃ sikkhāpadaṃ uddiseyyātha—"
msgstr "And, monks, this training rule should be recited thus:</p>"

#. HTML: </p><p><b class="rule">
#. REF: sc3
#, fuzzy
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc73:1.1.16"
msgid "“Yo pana bhikkhu anvaddhamāsaṃ pātimokkhe uddissamāne evaṃ vadeyya—"
msgstr ""
"<h2 id=\"pannatti\">Final ruling</h2><p class=\"rule\"><a class=\"pts-vp-en\""
" id=\"BD.3.44\">BD.3.44</a><a class=\"wt-pa\">1331</a>‘During the half-"
"monthly recitation of the monastic code, a monk might say,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc73:1.1.17"
msgid ""
"‘idāneva kho ahaṃ jānāmi, ayampi kira dhammo suttāgato suttapariyāpanno "
"anvaddhamāsaṃ uddesaṃ āgacchatī’ti."
msgstr ""
"“Just now did I find out that this rule too has come down in the monastic "
"code, is included in the monastic code, and comes up for recitation every "
"half-month.”"

#. VAR: bhiyyo → bhiyyoti (s1-3) 
#. VAR: uttari cassa → uttariṃ cassa (bj) | uttariñcassa (s1-3)
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc73:1.1.18"
msgid ""
"Tañce bhikkhuṃ aññe bhikkhū jāneyyuṃ nisinnapubbaṃ iminā bhikkhunā "
"dvattikkhattuṃ pātimokkhe uddissamāne, ko pana vādo bhiyyo, na ca tassa "
"bhikkhuno aññāṇakena mutti atthi, yañca tattha āpattiṃ āpanno tañca "
"yathādhammo kāretabbo, uttari cassa moho āropetabbo—"
msgstr ""
"If other monks know that that monk has previously sat through at least two "
"or three recitations of the monastic code, then that monk is not let off "
"because of ignorance, and he is to be dealt with according to the rule. "
"Further, he should be charged with deception:"

#. VAR: manasi karosī’ti → manasikarosīti (s1-3, pts1) 
#. VAR: aṭṭhiṃ katvā → aṭṭhikatvā (bj, s1-3, pts1, mr)
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc73:1.1.19"
msgid ""
"‘tassa te, āvuso, alābhā, tassa te dulladdhaṃ, yaṃ tvaṃ pātimokkhe "
"uddissamāne na sādhukaṃ aṭṭhiṃ katvā manasi karosī’ti."
msgstr ""
" “It’s a loss for you that you don’t pay proper attention when the monastic "
"code is being recited.”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc73:1.1.20"
msgid "Idaṃ tasmiṃ mohanake pācittiyan”ti."
msgstr ""
"And for the act of deception, he commits an offense entailing "
"confession.’”</p>"

